## Solution, Not Product | How AMOS™ Scales with Customers

AMOS™ is a solution, not a fixed product.

- Core capabilities form the stable foundation (asset management & compliance)
- Open, API-first architecture enables integration with:
  - ERP systems
  - E-procurement providers
  - Performance, fuel, ESG, and analytics tools

Customers extend AMOS™ without replacing their backbone or disrupting operations. This allows fleets to modernise at their own pace.

The top three global maritime ecommerce providers are SpecTec and AMOS™ partners.

